Document: VisualShaderNodeTransformDecompose
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodetransformdecompose.rst
Summary: Decomposes a 4×4 transform matrix into four vec3 values, each representing a row of the matrix.

Takes a 4×4 transform matrix and decomposes it into four vec3 values, one from each row of the matrix.